snippet.textDisplay: He didn’t climb , he descended down the building!🤦🏿‍♂️ Either way it was foolish!🤨 If he fell it would have made a mess! Or he would have fell on someone, which in turn would have caused the building owner to be liable. It would have also disrupted the actual tenants of the build having access in or out. Dude need to find another hobby!😒 IJS
